```java
// SETUP ORIGINAL LIST
List<String> original = new ArrayList<>();
original.add("blue");
original.add("red");

// CREATE COPY
List<String> copiedList = List.copyOf(original);

// ADD NEW ITEM TO ORIGINAL LIST
original.add("green");

// CHECK CONTENT
System.out.println(original);
// [blue, red, green]
System.out.println(copiedList);
// [blue, red]
```

